Model Your Enterprise with DARIOM
Lab Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Apply the DARIOM methodology (Discover, Assess, Redesign, Implement, Monitor) for enterprise security modeling
Create network diagrams using Draw.io to visualize enterprise architecture
Integrate MITRE ATT&CK Navigator to identify threat vectors
Document security improvements using Python automation
Develop actionable security assessment workflows
Prerequisites
Basic understanding of network security concepts
Familiarity with Linux command line
Basic Python programming knowledge
Understanding of enterprise network components
Lab Environment
Al Nafi Cloud Machine: Click Start Lab to access your pre-configured Linux environment with all necessary tools installed.

